Description: Command-line tool for window tiling on X11
 Tiler is a powerful command-line tool designed to automatically arrange
 and resize windows on X11 desktop environments. It provides flexible
 window tiling capabilities with support for various layout modes,
 aspect ratio control, and customizable margins.
 .
 Features include:
  * Automatic window arrangement and resizing
  * Application-specific window selection
  * Multiple tiling modes: horizontal, vertical, and grid layouts
  * Aspect ratio control for consistent window proportions
  * Configurable margins and spacing
  * Simple command-line interface
 .
 Perfect for users who want to organize their workspace efficiently,
 whether working with a few applications or managing dozens of windows
 simultaneously.
